Nigerian musician, David Adekele, popularly known as Davido, has announced that his Fiancée, Chioma, has recovered from coronavirus. Davido, who went into isolation when Chioma first tested positive for Coronavirus on March 27, made this announcement via his official Twitter handle. He said his fiancée, Chioma, had tested negative twice for Coronavirus. “Glory be to God. Chioma has now tested negative twice for COVID-19”, Davido said. He also thanked his fans for their prayers and support.